narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This series was an interesting and engaging group of speakers, but it could be improved in the future with a bit more inclusion of topics relevant to all grad students and labs within the social area.

The speaker lineup this year was great - diverse voices presenting a variety of topics, all with a high degree of excellence. The opportunity to lunch with speakers afterward also really contributed a lot.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I mean, this course is required for social psych students, but I would recommend to students from other areas too, based on the speaker quality this year.
